3. Persona

Introduction

In the realm of marketing and design, understanding the audience you are targeting is essential in crafting marketing strategies and the user experience. One extremely useful tool goes by the name of personas. Personas are fictional entities that represent your ideal customers, each embodying traits that your target market should possess. 


Dunkin Eisenhower:
    Dunkin Eisenhower is a 20-year-old finance major at NJIT. As is the nature of the finance major, Dunkin has an extremely hectic schedule and is always searching for things to do during his breaks. He heavily values self-care and believes in treating and rewarding himself for his hard work. He likes to discover and try new food places in the area with his group of friends as a way of spending time with them. 
